    /*                    CALLDATA OPERATIONS                     */
    /*.•°:°.´+˚.*°.˚:*.´•*.+°.•°:´*.´•*.•°.•°:°.´:•˚°.*°.˚:*.´+°.•*/

    // Calldata compression and decompression using selective run length encoding:
    // - Sequences of 0x00 (up to 128 consecutive).
    // - Sequences of 0xff (up to 32 consecutive).
    //
